These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: animation, family
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lemon
1. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
2. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | animation |
| Food       | kiwi | lemon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, subway
1. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
2. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | water |
| Transport      | subway     | bus  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, aristoff
There are 2 different nationalities: french, nigerian
1. the french is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
2. the french is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Cigar   | baccarat | aristoff  |
| Nationality   | french | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite
2 different games are played: monopoly, whist
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |
| Beverage   | sprite | fanta   |
| Game       | whist | monopoly |

