.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, cricket
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, april
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | badminton  | cricket |
| Birthday   | november | april |

